mployers will offer gratifying and educational opportunities for VMI Cadets  We are now posting internship opportunities on KeydetConnect  This is a free service if you are interested in posting internship opportunities to cadets  Recruiting and Interviewing on Campus  Post  Recruiting   Interviewing on campus is convenient and helpful to our cadets  Please consider a visit to VMI for recruitment purposes  Posting Job Announcements to Cadets Job Announcements in KeydetConnect will get wide dissemination to our cadets seeking full time employment opportunities  Please post any job announcements for approval here  Principles for Employment Professionals Employers are encouraged to follow the National Association of Colleges and Employers  NACE  principles for professional conduct in all recruiting activities with Virginia Military Institute  The principles are outlined at the following website  http www naceweb org Driving Directions are available for your convenience  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 